title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-22-2013 FRI
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-22-2013 FRI



Friday, November 22, 2013


Nuclear Option Hypocrisy



 
 

 - 9AM hour

Mike talks about Harry Reid's implementation of the nuclear option 
   thereby changing the Senate rules on filibustering judicial nominees.

      Also the hypocrisy of Obama, Biden and Reid on the issue is revealed in their 2005 comments.



 - 10AM hour

1. Mike provides a stark example of global warming indoctrination via a fifth grade assignment

      in a Colorado elementary school.


2. How media is covering the "knockout" phenomena.





 - 11AM hour

Movie Review: Mike and Christian Toto review "Enough Said" and
      "Dallas Buyers Club." 
             Be sure to follow Christian on his blog: http://daddylibrium.com/
